Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BetfairDataObject
    Interface designed for any object that contains betfair data.
    IBetFairCore
    Interface defining methods that the implementation of betfair must implement
    ISimpleBetFair
    Interface for classes that are to provide simple interaction with objects implementing IBetFairCore
    Observable
    A interface version of the Observable abstract class.
    Observer
    My version of Javas Observer interface.
    PredictionModel
    Interface defining core methods required for any sport PredictionModel
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BetfairCore
    BetFairCore is a class that implements all the BetFair API methods in the IBetFairCore interface.
    BetfairGameObject
    Object representing the required information for games, extracted from the Betfair API.
    BetfairMarketData
    Object representing the information extracted from Betfair markets
    BetfairMarketDataContainer
    This class is used to hold probablity data.
    BetfairMarketItem
    This class represents a market and the probabilities that its runners
    BetfairMarketObject
    This class is used to represent Markets in the form of its general information
    BetfairMarketRunnerDataContainer
    Class that represents a collection of a runners probability data
    BetfairProbabilityItem
    This class represents probabilitiy objects, which are composed of timestamps, values and the name of the runner they are for
    BetfairSportObject
    This class is used to represent sports
    DataAnalysis
    This class is an intermediary class for data analysis.
    DataIO
    This class receives live Betfair data and it collects and formats it.
    DataManager
    This class is used to manage data regarding BetFairs responses.
    EventList
    This class is used for passing events from DataRecorder to DataAnalysis
    FootballPredictionModel
    This class is used to predict game events for football from given probabilities and football.
    GameRecorder
    Class responsible for tracking games and storing the data from their play to files.
    PredictionModelFactory
    Factory for making prediction models.
    PredictionModelUtil
    Utility class used for PredictionModel.
    ProgramOptions
    This class is used to store the state of the GUI options.
    SimpleBetfair
    This class communicates with the BetFairCore class, takes the output and it sorts, parses and then returns it's results in an easy to read String format.
    TestFile
    This class is used for communication with the test file.
    ViewUpdate
    This class is used to hold data that is pushed up from the DataAnalysis class to the AnalysisView
